<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Admin Login - <%= siteName %></title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/main.css" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/public/img/logo-exhub.png" />
  <script src="/public/js/protect.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body class="page-dark">

  <%- include('partials/nav', { active: 'admin' }) %>

  <main class="center-wrap">
    <div class="card" style="max-width: 420px; width: 100%;">
      <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:12px;">
        <img
          src="/public/img/logo-exhub.png"
          alt="logo"
          style="width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;margin-bottom:8px;"
        />
        <h1 style="margin:0 0 6px;">Admin Panel Login</h1>
        <p class="helper-text">
          Halaman ini hanya untuk staff yang memiliki kredensial admin.
          Login menggunakan username &amp; password yang tersimpan di
          <code>ADMIN_USER</code> dan <code>ADMIN_PASS</code> (Environment Variables).
        </p>
      </div>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-error">
          <div class="alert-title">Login gagal</div>
          <div><%= error %></div>
        </div>
      <% } %>

      <form method="post" action="/admin/login" style="margin-top:12px;">
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-bottom:12px;">
          <div>
            <label style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);display:block;margin-bottom:4px;">
              Username
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="username"
              required
              autocomplete="username"
              class="input"
              placeholder="Admin username"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);display:block;margin-bottom:4px;">
              Password
            </label>
            <input
              type="password"
              name="password"
              required
              autocomplete="current-password"
              class="input"
              placeholder="Admin password"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">
          Login as Admin
        </button>
      </form>

      <p class="helper-text" style="margin-top:10px;font-size:12px;text-align:center;">
        Kredensial tidak disimpan di database / Redis.
        Semua validasi terjadi di server menggunakan environment variables.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <span>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= siteName %> • Admin Area</span>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
